column5: Reach length of approx 25 m breached at an earthen embankment constructed by local public at village Belpara
column11: Reported by Gaon Pradhan, Boko Revenue Circle. Also, inspected by staff of Boko Rev. Circle and Field Staff of W.R Dept., Chhaygaon-Boko W.R Sub-Division. It is to be mentioned here that it is not a designated embankment of W.R Dept.
